{"tid":2014374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"華裔科學家李飛飛加入Twitter，專責打擊假消息，曾稱“不忘初心”","createTime":"2020-05-13T04:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T11:21:59.000Z","uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"48c687b29a456f01060b9d90c3af33992b95dc97","tid":2014374,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"世界中國化<br />\n<br />\n不忘初心，牢記使命，是中共十九大提出的口號。李飛飛也十分讚同。不知會否協助twitter打壓黃絲呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcdmYH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcdmYH8.jpg&h=af52d3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0ONUgu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0ONUgu.jpg&h=656194cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n～～～～～～～～～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=36b3bec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a>"},{"pid":"17ddd94250300c9ec4df3ade22841af5d910e023","tid":2014374,"uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"疑似親共 但睇佢資料條友堅係勁"},{"pid":"113937c4d39e1d718b4d84d5316d8d837b056724","tid":2014374,"uid":48040,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"17ddd94250300c9ec4df3ade22841af5d910e023","tid":2014374,"uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"疑似親共 但睇佢資料條友堅係勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"親共而且勁，大鍋"},{"pid":"0a3f3d07809ccdb445f043a5e532b9317b321851","tid":2014374,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家無藉口唔打國際線喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=dfac7e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n<br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=5c2418bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n另有手足會係佢Twitter Account 每日更新任務:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTweetingforHK&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=015780f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TweetingforHK</a><br />\n<br />\n或者download 香城online 個app 都有Twitter 任務做<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKOnlinePortal&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=319f7abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKOnlinePortal</a><br />\n<br />\nLike retweet reply<br />\nTask2係國際戰線，唔好淨係推Task 1,Task2都好重要。<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n將Twitter 變成日常，每人每日做少少。<br />\n每人嘅一小步加埋就係一大步。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩先有用，所以咩都試下咩都做下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc0a912862d50908e40330181dd1b649059e35","tid":2014374,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T07:39:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"29507a43e7bea39694e5ab3d874bb5360f1f2a57","tid":2014374,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl